{"tid":2146613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"睇下歷史，到時香港人會唔會成為下一批猶太人？","createTime":"2020-08-08T17:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T18:55:13.000Z","uid":231886,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1053c037a11e47d0ecfefee3abd9dfefd18dbcf3","tid":2146613,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T17:00:34.000Z","msg":"1939年英國開始經濟制裁德國。<br />\n<span class=\"red\">1940年時大多數猶太人仍保持樂觀地生活在德國，因為他們相信暴政終將&quot;安靜地&quot;滅亡</span>，只需暫時忍耐被沒收收音機。 <br />\n1945年總共600萬猶太人被屠殺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*75年後&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n2020年，美國開始制裁中國<br />\n2020年，香港人在西區體育館和亞博變成臨時醫院/限聚令/口罩令的同時熱烈慶祝林鄭被制裁，然後繼續安靜守法地返工搵食。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當大家都好驚支那，又成日話武力不平等，制裁就開始，到底支那會唔會發難玩封國？<br />\n64時佢地做過一次封國，習近平咁撚on9唔好以為支那做唔出再次封國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd1df4a01ca59b0c9abc1dd4252195580875059","tid":2146613,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T17:02:32.000Z","msg":"生係香港人，死係香港鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d855986fb4c05e1629ee352ebaf8fa3a8fd54edf","tid":2146613,"uid":143343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T17:03:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bb5aebe6eac1aea4150ef1d84e21e01a2f376b0","tid":2146613,"uid":115096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T17:04:10.000Z","msg":"猶太人一條心<br />\n香港人有藍屍"},{"pid":"64f2eb093011c8cb719a8e0ed74d6c310e446c12","tid":2146613,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T17:04:28.000Z","msg":"逃生門緊"},{"pid":"e0dcce0bb609d44e084ce6b57a97bfd79dbe4c31","tid":2146613,"uid":231886,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d855986fb4c05e1629ee352ebaf8fa3a8fd54edf","tid":2146613,"uid":143343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"scor